** Prerequisites:

libgmp3-dev libssl-dev libdb4.6-dev

On debian just

apt-get install libdb4.6-dev libgmp3-dev libssl-dev

** Compiling:

gcc -g bc_key.c -ldb -lgmp -lcrypto -o bc_key

** Usage:

./bc_key BITCOIN_ADDRESS /path/to/wallet.dat


Example: ./bc_key 1qZGQG5Ls66oBbtLt3wPMa6zfq7CJ7f12 /home/dirtyfilthy/.bitcoin/wallet.dat

